        "question_adqrYK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How does the heated curler work?",
            "answer": "<p>The curler uses gentle, controlled heat to lift and curl your lashes naturally — without clamping or pinching. Just turn it on, let it warm up for about 10 seconds, then gently press it against your lashes from base to tip. Hold for 5–10 seconds and release. Your lashes will stay lifted all day with a soft, natural curl.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_TDP7NK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the heat safe for my lashes?",
            "answer": "<p>Absolutely. The heat is specifically designed to be warm enough to curl your lashes effectively, but never hot enough to damage them or your skin. It's gentler than traditional clamping curlers, which can pinch, snap lashes, or pull them out.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hPGXCN": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I use the eyebrow trimmer?",
            "answer": "<p>Just switch attachments and turn it on. Glide the precision trimmer gently along the edges of your brows to clean up stray hairs and define your shape. The blade is small and precise, making it easy to get clean, sharp lines — even for beginners.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_7Rxwez": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How is it powered?",
            "answer": "<p>The device is USB rechargeable — just plug it in with the included cable when the battery runs low. A full charge lasts for multiple uses, and there are no batteries to replace. Perfect for travel and everyday use on the go.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_Pzgd7t": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it good for beginners?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! It's specifically designed to be beginner-friendly. The heated curler doesn't require any technique — just press and hold. The trimmer's precision design makes brow shaping easy and forgiving. You'll get salon-quality results from the very first use.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
